* Download systemC source code v2.3.3
https://accellera.org/images/downloads/standards/systemc/systemc-2.3.3.tar.gz

* Compile and generate systemC libraries
$> cmake -B build -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=<xxx>/built
$> cd build
$> make
$> make install

* Use script
$> gen_sysc.sh

Install path: systemc-2.3.3-built

